title: Did you tell Kamala Harris Jacob Blake that she was "proud of him "?
subtitle: The candidate for Vice President met with the Blake family in Wisconsin after police shot Blake several times in the back.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: Kamala Harris, United States, met Jacob Blake - a mummy who claimed to have "raped a woman" - and told him that she was "proud of him" in September 2020.
